<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="37r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l25"><expan>Vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dıenſt beuor VVeinmar Eker ʒu <expan>Saldenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_74_r1l26"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eker als Jr vns vor <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / wıe Jr eẅch habt muſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l27"><expan>entſıcʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> von des angrıffs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . als vns frıdel nıemantſgenoſʒ vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l28">ſein <expan>geſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> getan <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc Darauf wır eẅch <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mals </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l29"><expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . daʒ wır eẅch von der ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l30"><expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan> gewartt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd hinfür keins <expan>arg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gewarten <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l31">vnd eẅch <expan>deſgleıch<ex>en</ex></expan> auch getrawten . Alſo habt Jr vns nu <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l32">vvıe wır eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>klagt</expan> <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> des Jr ʒu <expan>merklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſcheden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r1l33"><expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeyt etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd wıſſen niht </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_75" id="37v"/>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l1">daʒ wır eẅch <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>klagt</expan> oder ʒu ſchaden bracht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l2"><expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mıt fleıſʒ . Jr lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> on rede vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l3">ſprüch . vnd ʒıeht vns noch den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vnwıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ʒu das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l4"><expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vmb eẅch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> Deẅcht eẅch <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> . daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l5">Jr ʒu vns ıht ʒu <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> Jr vns on red niht gelaſſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l6">möcht . ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eıns <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> ſeın an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l7">den <expan>ſtett<ex>en</ex></expan> da wır das pıllıch tun <expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . hett Jr <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l8"><expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> ıht ʒe <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır eẅch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>ſcheınbott<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l10">mıt <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt 
<add><ab facs="#facs_75_r2l9">von </ab></add> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> ʒu </del> <expan>freẅntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> ſleẅnıgs <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l11"><expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des Reıchs <expan>Rıcht<ex>er</ex></expan> bey vns ʒu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan> wenn wır des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l12">ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> . ſo dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ʒu den Jr ʒe <expan>ſprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett anheım ſınt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l13">on <expan>geu<ex>er</ex>de</expan> . Vnd getrawn eẅch wol . Jr lat eẅch des von vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l14"><expan>benüg<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd lat vns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eẅr <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_75_r2l15"><expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> bey dem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ııȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Mıchahel<ex>is</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="37r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Weinmar Eker zu <expan>Saldenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><add><expan>Uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienst bevor.</add>
<expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Eker, als ir uns vor
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt, wie ir ewch habt mussen
                                <expan>entsicze<ex>n</ex></expan> von des angriffs
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als uns Fridel Niemantsgenosz und
                        sein <expan>gesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> getan <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etc., darauf wir ewch
                            <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> mals
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> daz wir ewch von der sache
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> keins <expan>arge<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        gewartt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und hinfür keins
                            <expan>arg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> gewarten <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        ewch <expan>desgleich<ex>en</ex></expan> auch getrawten. Also habt ir uns nu
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, wie wir ewch
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>klagt</expan>
<expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> des ir zu <expan>merklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        scheden <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyt etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nom<ex>en</ex></expan> und wissen niht, <pb facs="#facs_75" id="37v"/>daz wir ewch <expan>yend<ex>er</ex>t</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>klagt</expan> oder zu schaden bracht
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit
                        fleisz, ir lat uns <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> on rede und sprüch und
                        zieht uns noch den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>kein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>unwill<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> zu; das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> umb ewch
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. Dewcht ewch
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>, daz ir zu uns iht zu
                                <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett,
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ir uns on red niht gelassen möcht, so
                                <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eins <expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> sein an den <expan>stett<ex>en,</ex></expan>
                        da wir das pillich tun <expan>sull<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, hett ir
                                <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan> iht ze <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewch <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <add>von</add>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> slewnigs
                            <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                            <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu
                            <expan>Nur<ex>emberg,</ex></expan> wenn wir des ermant
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so die
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, zu den ir ze
                            <expan>sprech<ex>en</ex></expan> hett, anheim sint on
                                <expan>gev<ex>er</ex>de</expan>. Und getrawn ewch wol, ir lat ewch
                        des von uns <expan>benüg<ex>en;</ex></expan> und lat uns
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr
                            <expan>frewntl<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        bey dem <expan>bott<ex>en.</ex></expan>
<expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> iii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Michahel<ex>is</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
